      "releaseNotes": "We continuously update StoryReel with new features and optimize the experience, so you can enjoy better viewing moments.\n\nWhat's new in this update:\n\nPerformance improvements for smoother playback;\n\nRegularly adding more exciting short dramas – stay tuned for non‑stop stories!\n\nDo you like StoryReel? We'd love to hear your feedback. Please rate us. Your feedback helps us improve.",
